arget":"recyDlo13a3T5DDGh","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMCdhqDGkZDPF39","target":"recLuZtSmAO6erIsc","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMCdhqDGkZDPF39","target":"rectAKOMFVWfGYUGW","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMCdhqDGkZDPF39","target":"rec0rm6yYA4YUQrkh","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMCdhqDGkZDPF39","target":"recVua5TkKSl3y6Ol","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMCdhqDGkZDPF39","target":"recsZrzcKXJ8R2JCb","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMCdhqDGkZDPF39","target":"recRxBBePxyyV6TFO","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMCdhqDGkZDPF39","target":"recN4jruK7QVakoJh","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMCdhqDGkZDPF39","target":"recWjPbc94D45lkIZ","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMCdhqDGkZDPF39","target":"recn47IzNNlhvTtXK","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMCdhqDGkZDPF39","target":"recKRQCw7nVGXU2A8","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMCdhqDGkZDPF39","target":"reci0DJ1lahPFlLir","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMCdhqDGkZDPF39","target":"recasO0QihALHPcLg","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMCdhqDGkZDPF39","target":"rec5dSSsOutWlH2fW","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMCdhqDGkZDPF39","target":"recM1lN580CYvi2y8","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMCdhqDGkZDPF39","target":"recLcxRZbz3yIQB7b","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"rec90Wof7WPbqj0Dy","ref":"Num.34.1","text":"And the LORD spake unto Moses, saying,","year":-1452},{"id":"recW7ltIe0dNCvMFt","ref":"Num.34.2","text":"Command the children of Israel, and say unto them, When ye come into the land of Canaan; (this is the land that shall fall unto you for an inheritance, even the land of Canaan with the coasts thereof:)","year":-1452},{"id":"recimtM0GoJoK78Hx","ref":"Num.34.3","text":"Then your south quarter shall be from the wilderness of Zin along by the coast of Edom, and your south border shall be the outmost coast of the salt sea eastward:","year":-1452},{"id":"recYy9IF8lVkpD9iX","ref":"Num.34.4","text":"And your border shall turn from the south to the ascent of Akrabbim, and pass on to Zin: and the going forth thereof shall be from the south to Kadeshbarnea, and shall go on to Hazaraddar, and pass on to Azmon:","year":-1452},{"id":"rec7LTmXbPw87OVI4","ref":"Num.34.5","text":"And the border shall fetch a compass from Azmon unto the river of Egypt, and the goings out of it shall be at the sea.","year":-1452},{"id":"recPsAo0fTNlxxQXa","ref":"Num.34.6","text":"And as for the western border, ye shall even have the great sea for a border: this shall be your west border.","year":-1452},{"id":"recAUXJzGIawou7Vk","ref":"Num.34.7","text":"And this shall be your north border: from the great sea ye shall point out for you mount Hor:","year":-1452},{"id":"recStf3ZZSSqugUaV","ref":"Num.34.8","text":"From mount Hor ye shall point out your border unto the entrance of Hamath; and the goings forth of the border shall be to Zedad:","year":-1452}]}
